# ==========================================
# SCI PK VIDEO & AUDIO EXCLUSIONS
# ==========================================

# 1. Ignore Manim's default media output directories
media/
**/media/

# 2. Ignore all video file formats globally (any folder, any depth)
*.mp4
*.mov
*.avi
*.mkv
*.webm
*.gif

# 3. Ignore audio files (voiceovers, SFX, music)
*.wav
*.mp3
*.m4a
*.flac

# 4. Ignore video editor temporary files (Premiere / After Effects)
**/Adobe Premiere Pro Auto-Save/
*.prproj
*.aep
*.aepx